VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT allUsers|allAuthenticatedUsers
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:role\s*=\s*"roles/storage\.objectViewer".*allUsers|allAuthenticatedUsers && MISSING:# intentional|# static-website|website\s*\{
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects GCS bucket IAM bindings that grant access to allUsers or allAuthenticatedUsers.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for GCP Storage Bucket Publicly Accessible.
